extendedInfo.description: This program reads your Master Subsidy Lock (MSL) code for your CDMA Android phone. It requires root to read this code.This application will only work on HTC CDMA devices like the Hero, EVO and Incredible.MSL may be called the SPC (Service Programming Code).* Requires network access for AdMob ads.
